title: Groundswell
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee, food, and baked goods in the Hamline Midway neighborhood of Saint Paul. Offers various vegetarian choices. Vegans could get the banana bread, soymilk for granola, a vegan platter (tempeh steak with quinoa tabouli, chili roasted chickpeas, fresh greens, and lime cilantro dressing). Other items can be made vegan by request, such as the beet salad minus cheese.
